"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1929207-paris-2024-olympics-female-athletes\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"AnOlympicsbroadcasting chief has urged camera operators to avoid \\\"sexist\\\" filming of female athletes.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 103, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AnOlympicsbroadcasting chief\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"camera operators\", \"from\": 39, \"to\": 55}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"sexist\\\" filming\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 81}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 85, \"to\": 100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris 2024 Olympics have already made ground-breaking changes to reach gender parity - and now its official broadcaster is tackling \\\"unconscious biases\\\" when covering women's sports.\", \"from\": 104, \"to\": 290, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 114, \"end\": 127, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2024 Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ground-breaking changes\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"gender parity\", \"from\": 179, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"its official broadcaster\", \"from\": 203, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"unconscious biases\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 259}, {\"ngram\": \"women's sports\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Games having got underway on Friday, head of Olympic Broadcasting Services (OBS) Yiannis Exarchos has been vocal about men's and women's sports being filmed in the same way.\", \"from\": 292, \"to\": 474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 346, \"end\": 375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Broadcasting Services\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}, {\"begin\": 390, \"end\": 398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.21292013311444e-18, \"text\": \"Exarchos\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Exarch\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 297, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"Friday\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 336}, {\"ngram\": \"head\", \"from\": 338, \"to\": 342}, {\"ngram\": \"OBS\", \"from\": 377, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 420, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 430, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"the same way\", \"from\": 461, \"to\": 473}]}, {\"sentence\": \"OBS is responsible for the TV coverage of the Olympics, with its images shared with rights holders around the world.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 591, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 475, \"end\": 478, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999981769179, \"rank\": 1.8231904939592509e-09, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the TV coverage\", \"from\": 498, \"to\": 513}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 529}, {\"ngram\": \"its images\", \"from\": 536, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"rights holders\", \"from\": 559, \"to\": 573}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 581, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exarchos revealed that the organisation has already updated its guidelines for camera operators, most of whom are men.\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exarchos\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisation\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"its guidelines\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 667}, {\"ngram\": \"camera operators\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 710}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And he wants to avoid both stereotypes and sexism from creeping into the coverage over the next two weeks.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 818, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"both stereotypes\", \"from\": 734, \"to\": 750}, {\"ngram\": \"sexism\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"the coverage\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 793}, {\"ngram\": \"the next two weeks\", \"from\": 799, \"to\": 817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Unfortunately, in some events they [women] are still being filmed in a way that you can identify that stereotypes and sexism remains, even from the way in which some camera operators are framing differently men and women athletes,\\\" the OBS chief executive told reporters in Paris on Sunday.\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1060, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"score\": 0.9999999981769179, \"rank\": 1.8231904939592509e-09, \"text\": \"OBS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Broadcasting_Services\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974716047, \"rank\": 2.52836219724172e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some events\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 850}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 862}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"stereotypes\", \"from\": 923, \"to\": 934}, {\"ngram\": \"sexism\", \"from\": 939, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 972}, {\"ngram\": \"some camera operators\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"men and women athletes\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"reporters\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1091}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1104, \"to\": 1110}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Women athletes are not there because they are more attractive or sexy or whatever.\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1196, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Women athletes\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are there because they are elite athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"elite athletes\", \"from\": 1229, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Exarchos explained how the problem was primarily down to \\\"unconscious bias\\\", which meant camera operators and TV editors tend to show more close-up shots of women than of men.\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Exarchos\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1255}, {\"ngram\": \"the problem\", \"from\": 1270, \"to\": 1281}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"unconscious bias\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1321}, {\"ngram\": \"camera operators\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"TV editors\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1367}, {\"ngram\": \"more close-up shots\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"men\", \"from\": 1418, \"to\": 1421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1468, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Discovery+is\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the new home\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1467}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1533, \"end\": 1538, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource